content.rendered: Today’s guest is the HOW TO expert and 17 year year old YouTuber, Ella Elbells! We show you how to make one of our favorite snacks in this video, a POWER PROTEIN BALL BITE!!! Perfect for school, work, afternoon energy boost, etc. Easy to make, and store for the whole week.
